mbti_signals.shift_explanation: Slight T->F shift showing concern for better collaboration. Slight P->J shift requesting more structured handoffs and actionable next steps.

big5_signals.notable: Conscientiousness elevated above baseline - focused on process improvement and structured communication

learnings: User values actionable handoffs with open-ended questions that synthesize memory and assessments
Prefers entry statements that identify gaps and drive next steps rather than just summarizing
Wants assistant to proactively identify what's most important across all context

meta_observations.what_worked: Assistant immediately understood and implemented the feedback about capping with questions
meta_observations.what_didnt: Response was cut off mid-sentence, suggesting need for more concise delivery
